00:23:23.468 --> 00:23:25.036 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: I feel like
we're in an AA meeting.

00:23:25.103 --> 00:23:27.973 line:95%,end
Hi, my name is Christi,
and I'm a dance mom.

00:23:28.039 --> 00:23:29.374 line:5%,start
Here we are--the day the music video,

00:23:29.441 --> 00:23:32.411 line:5%,start
and it's so amazing to be in Hollywood.

00:23:32.477 --> 00:23:35.013 line:95%,end
<i>All I can think is, how did we get here?</i>

00:23:35.080 --> 00:23:38.016 line:95%,end
We are a bunch of moms
with kids from Pittsburgh.

00:23:38.083 --> 00:23:40.585 line:95%,end
Like, how did we end up here?

