00:23:47.926 --> 00:23:49.761 line:95%,end
You're at a soundstage.

00:23:49.828 --> 00:23:52.197 line:95%,end
You are doing a real video shoot.

00:23:52.264 --> 00:23:54.299 line:5%,start
Today, the girls are going to get
their first taste

00:23:54.366 --> 00:23:55.934 line:5%,start
