00:23:56.001 --> 00:23:58.103 line:5%,start
This is everything
that they have worked for.

00:23:58.170 --> 00:24:00.572 line:95%,end
<i>They just need to apply</i>
<i>everything I've taught them,</i>

00:24:00.639 --> 00:24:02.307 line:95%,end
<i>remember everything they've learned,</i>

00:24:02.374 --> 00:24:03.375 line:95%,end
<i>and they'll do fine.</i>

00:24:03.442 --> 00:24:05.811 line:95%,end
I think all of these boys
have worked before.

00:24:06.378 --> 00:24:07.546 line:95%,end
<i>They've all done videos.</i>

00:24:07.612 --> 00:24:08.880 line:95%,end
<i>They're used to doing this.</i>

00:24:08.947 --> 00:24:11.583 line:95%,end
<i>I want you to be</i>
<i>just as professional as they are.</i>

00:24:11.650 --> 00:24:12.617 line:95%,end
Okay?

00:24:12.684 --> 00:24:14.920 line:5%,start
The girls are dancing with boys.

00:24:14.986 --> 00:24:17.122 line:95%,end
<i>And the girls are really excited</i>
<i>about that part.</i>

00:24:17.189 --> 00:24:18.523 line:95%,end
<i>It's really adorable.</i>

00:24:18.590 --> 00:24:21.460 line:95%,end
ABBY: Thank you all
for working with my girls today,

00:24:21.526 --> 00:24:23.695 line:95%,end
and have fun, and make them look good.

00:24:23.762 --> 00:24:25.530 line:95%,end
You know, that's the guy's job, right?

00:24:25.597 --> 00:24:27.432 line:95%,end
I'm watching the boys partner my girls,

00:24:27.499 --> 00:24:28.834 line:95%,end
and I'm a little bit concerned.

00:24:28.900 --> 00:24:30.469 line:95%,end
<i>First of all, they're not very big.</i>

00:24:30.535 --> 00:24:32.971 line:95%,end
A guy should be about six inches taller
than his partner.

00:24:33.038 --> 00:24:36.041 line:95%,end
RAY: Phillip, we're going to put you
with Mackenzie.

00:24:36.107 --> 00:24:37.509 line:95%,end
Mackenzie is with this little boy.

00:24:37.576 --> 00:24:40.712 line:95%,end
He's darling, and I'm sure
he's very good at what he does.

00:24:40.779 --> 00:24:44.115 line:95%,end
But he has to drop her down
to a split and pick her back up.

00:24:44.182 --> 00:24:46.017 line:95%,end
I don't think he could pick up
his backpack.

00:24:46.084 --> 00:24:48.186 line:95%,end
One, two, three, and four,

00:24:48.253 --> 00:24:50.655 line:95%,end
back, five, six, seven, and eight.

00:24:50.722 --> 00:24:54.226 line:95%,end
MELISSA: We're watching the boys and
the girls starting to rehearse together,

00:24:54.292 --> 00:24:57.062 line:95%,end
and Mackenzie's partner
is the same size as her.

00:24:57.729 --> 00:25:00.832 line:95%,end
<i>And he is a bit clueless.</i>

00:25:00.899 --> 00:25:03.502 line:95%,end
RAY: Five, six, seven, eight.

00:25:03.568 --> 00:25:06.037 line:95%,end
One and two, three and four,

00:25:06.104 --> 00:25:08.206 line:95%,end
five, six, seven, eight.

