Let's try it again, okay,

00:25:10.809 --> 00:25:12.444 line:95%,end
just so we can get it all
in our heads and partner together.

00:25:12.511 --> 00:25:14.279 line:95%,end
-What's wrong?
-What's wrong?

00:25:14.813 --> 00:25:16.081 line:95%,end
You knew it perfectly.

00:25:16.147 --> 00:25:17.349 line:95%,end
I can't do it.

00:25:17.415 --> 00:25:18.517 line:95%,end
Why?

00:25:19.451 --> 00:25:22.187 line:95%,end
Okay, what--yes, you can.

00:25:22.787 --> 00:25:25.056 line:95%,end
-Mackenzie, you look good.
-RAY: Mackenzie, you look great, girl.

00:25:25.857 --> 00:25:27.192 line:95%,end
Do you want to try it one more time?

00:25:27.259 --> 00:25:28.660 line:95%,end
You're ready to do it, Mackenzie.

00:25:28.727 --> 00:25:30.095 line:95%,end
-What's wrong, babe?
-MACKENZIE: No, I'm not.

00:25:30.161 --> 00:25:31.162 line:95%,end
I'm not ready.

00:25:31.229 --> 00:25:32.564 line:95%,end
-MELISSA: Yes, you are.
-I'm not ready.

00:25:32.631 --> 00:25:34.199 line:95%,end
Mom, I'm not ready.

00:25:35.367 --> 00:25:36.568 line:95%,end
I'm not.

00:25:36.635 --> 00:25:38.003 line:95%,end
I'm not ready.

00:25:38.069 --> 00:25:39.137 line:95%,end
-I don't want to...
-MELISSA: Yes, you are.

00:25:39.204 --> 00:25:40.038 line:95%,end
RAY: All right, let's keep going.

00:25:40.105 --> 00:25:42.541 line:95%,end
-Ready. Here we go.
